### Simple string input
POST http://localhost:8088/responses
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "input": "What's the weather in Vancouver?"
}

### Implicit user input with simple string content
POST http://localhost:8088/responses
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "input": [
        {
            "content": "What's the weather in Vancouver?"
        }
    ]
}

### Implicit user input with list of ItemContent
POST http://localhost:8088/responses
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "input": [
        {
            "content": [
                {
                    "type": "input_text",
                    "text": "What's the weather in Vancouver?"
                }
            ]
        }
    ]
}

### Explicit input
POST http://localhost:8088/responses
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "input": [
        {
            "type": "message",
            "role": "system",
            "content": [
                {
                    "type": "input_text",
                    "text": "You are a helpful assistant that provides weather information."
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "message",
            "role": "user",
            "content": [
                {
                    "type": "input_text",
                    "text": "What's the weather in Vancouver?"
                }
            ]
        }
    ]
}

